title: Taiho Shichau zo (TV) (You're Under Arrest (1996))
synopsis: Tokyo Highway Patrolwomen Natsumi and Miyuki get off to a bad start when Miyuki busts Natsumi for reckless moped driving on her way to work. Things get worse when they find out they're going to be partners!
